  "detailed_description": "Survive Or Die is a first-person survival game. It takes place in an open world that is full of traps and mysteries. You are an outlaw who has escaped from death in prison. Can you escape all the manhunts? Can you survive the pitfalls the mysterious valley holds at night?<br><br><br><br><strong>About the game</strong><br>Just before your execution in the electric chair, a riot broke out in the prison. You take advantage of it and break out of prison. You find yourself in a very strange mountain valley that hides many secrets.<br><br><br><strong>What awaits you:</strong><br>- Crafting<br>- making items<br>- building dwellings<br>- fighting<br>- fighting for survival<br>- exploration",
  "about_the_game": "Survive Or Die is a first-person survival game. It takes place in an open world that is full of traps and mysteries. You are an outlaw who has escaped from death in prison. Can you escape all the manhunts? Can you survive the pitfalls the mysterious valley holds at night?<br><br><br><br><strong>About the game</strong><br>Just before your execution in the electric chair, a riot broke out in the prison. You take advantage of it and break out of prison. You find yourself in a very strange mountain valley that hides many secrets.<br><br><br><strong>What awaits you:</strong><br>- Crafting<br>- making items<br>- building dwellings<br>- fighting<br>- fighting for survival<br>- exploration",
